Package: ACcalibration
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the number of calibration points for new areas.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peter Roosjen
Maintainer: Peter Roosjen <peter.roosjen@agrocares.com>
Description: This packages 1) extracts cropland areas for a area of interest, 2) extracts covariables for it, and 3) calculates the requiered number of samples to for calibration.
